    dc:description "Figure 1. Morphology of Modicella guangxiensis. A Sporocarps and its habitat; B Dried yellowish sporocarps; C-F Intact sporangia; G, H Sporangiospores; I, J, K Different kinds of hyphae. Scale bar A-B = 5 mm; C-F = 25 μm; G-H = 20 μm; I-K = 10 μm. C, D, G, I. in purified water; E, J, K. in 1 % Congo Red; F, H. in Cotton Blue; Photos by Guang-fu Mou, from M 2021081545 (holotype IBK!)." ;
